<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<!--
	RELEASE (Matt / Sparkle) entitlements. 2026-06-14 CloudKit env split.
	Plain ASCII only: codesign's AMFI entitlements parser is stricter than
	plutil and rejects non-ASCII / commented-out keys (it failed 0.2.51 the
	first time on this file). Keep this file ASCII and comment-light.

	WHY A SEPARATE FILE: Voxhora-Mac.entitlements is also used by deploy.sh
	(Patrick's Debug). Putting the Production CloudKit key in that shared file
	would flip Patrick's Debug Mac to Production too and hide his Development
	data. So the Release pipeline (release.sh final codesign + the Release
	config CODE_SIGN_ENTITLEMENTS in project.yml) seals against THIS file
	instead; Debug keeps Voxhora-Mac.entitlements = Development.

	CURRENT STATE: identical to Voxhora-Mac.entitlements (Development; no
	icloud-container-environment key). The product is NOT flipped to
	Production yet. Per the HARD RULE, Matt's Development data must be
	exported and verified in Production BEFORE the flip.

	TO FLIP THE RELEASE BUILD TO PRODUCTION (migration Step 3): add an
	icloud-container-environment entitlement set to the string Production
	inside this dict (key name com.apple.developer.icloud-container-environment),
	then run release.sh. The embedded Dev-ID Direct profile already authorizes
	the Production value (verified 2026-06-14). See the
	voxhora_cloudkit_prod_migration_tool memory + the migration handoff.
	-->
	<key>com.apple.application-identifier</key>
	<string>S4GM27H6N5.com.patrickfagerberg.voxhora.mac</string>
	<key>com.apple.developer.team-identifier</key>
	<string>S4GM27H6N5</string>
	<key>com.apple.developer.icloud-container-identifiers</key>
	<array>
		<string>iCloud.com.patrickfagerberg.voxhora</string>
	</array>
	<key>com.apple.developer.icloud-services</key>
	<array>
		<string>CloudKit</string>
		<string>CloudDocuments</string>
	</array>
	<key>com.apple.developer.ubiquity-container-identifiers</key>
	<array>
		<string>iCloud.com.patrickfagerberg.voxhora</string>
	</array>
	<key>com.apple.developer.aps-environment</key>
	<string>production</string>
	<key>com.apple.security.application-groups</key>
	<array>
		<string>group.com.patrickfagerberg.voxhora</string>
	</array>
	<key>keychain-access-groups</key>
	<array>
		<string>S4GM27H6N5.com.patrickfagerberg.voxhora.shared</string>
	</array>
	<key>com.apple.security.automation.apple-events</key>
	<true/>
	<key>com.apple.security.cs.allow-jit</key>
	<true/>
	<key>com.apple.security.cs.disable-library-validation</key>
	<true/>
</dict>
</plist>
